{"description": "Structured output for context relevance evaluation.", "properties": {"rating": {"description": "Relevance rating (0, 1, or 2)", "title": "Rating", "type": "integer"}}, "required": ["rating"], "title": "ContextRelevanceOutput", "type": "object"}Do not use single quotes in your response but double quotes,properly escaped with a backslash.

--------EXAMPLES-----------
